(22, 'current', '<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial Black" color="#ff0000" size="5"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial Black" color="#ff0000" size="5">Al- Wadia Current Deposit:</font><font face="Arial"><o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r <p class="MsoNormal"><span ><font face="Arial">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Al-Wadiah Current Account\r\nfollows the Principle of Islami Shariah wherein the bank is deemed as a keeper\r\nand trustee of funds as Al-Amana (on Trust). This deposit that operates by\r\ntaking permission from depositors would be taken to use their fund according to\r\nShariah Principle and depositors would not receive any kind of profit. As such\r\nthe bank is under obligation to return the entire money on demand by the\r\ncustomer. The account is not time barred i.e. Account Holder can withdraw money\r\nas many numbers of times as he wishes in a working day.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r <p class="MsoNormal"><span ><font face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial Black" size="4" color="#000099">Main\r Features:</font><font face="Arial" ><o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r <p class="MsoNormal"><ul><li><span ><font face="Arial">Halal way or without Riba\r (interest or usury) transaction</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">Unlimited deposit or withdrawal</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">No profit will be given</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">Cheque book facilities</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">ATM Card</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">Free online transaction</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">No Over Draft will be allowed in\r the account</font></span></li><li><font face="Arial"><span >SMS banking service includes\r balance inquires/Mini-statement by mobile phone.</span><span >&nbsp;</span></font></li></ul><font face="Arial"><o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial"><o