No\r minimum balance required</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">Partial\r waiver on VISA Debit Card</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">Cheque\r book facility.</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">Loan facility at\r\npreferential rates (Personal loan, Home loan, Auto loan).</font></span></li></ul></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r <p class="MsoNormal" ><span ><font face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r <p class="MsoNormal" ><span ><font face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r <p class="MsoNormal" ><b><font face="Arial Black" size="5" color="#ff0000">Resident Foreign\r\nCurrency Deposit (RFCD) Account:</font></b></p>\r\n\r <p class="MsoNormal"><span ><font face="Arial">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Resident\r\nForeign Currency Deposit (RFCD) Account is a foreign currency account in which\r\nfund is kept as deposit. Resident Bangladeshi Nationals can open this account\r\nwith foreign currency brought in at the time of return from travel abroad.\r\nMinimum amount required to open is USD 1,000 or equivalent currency in GBP\r\n&amp; Euro<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span ><font face="Arial"><br></font></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><span ><font face="Arial Black" size="4" color="#000099">Product Features:</font><font face="Arial" ><o:p></o:p></font></span></b></p>\r\n\r <p class="MsoNormal"><ul><li><span ><font face="Arial">Open\r in the form of USD, GBP &amp; EURO.</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">Deposit\r\nup to USD 5,000 or its equivalent brought in without any declaration can be\r credited to this account</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">Attractive\r\nInterest rate on Monthly minimum balance above USD 1,000 or GBP 500 or its\r equivalent</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">No\r Account maintenance fee.</font></span></li><li><span ><font face="Arial">International\r\nDebit Card facility against RFCD A