(7, 28200, 'available', 1, 352577, 338400, '<font face="Arial" size="3">\r\n\r\n<font size="4" color="#000099"><b>Manarah Hajj Deposit Scheme:</b></font><br><br>Manarah Hajj Deposit Scheme is a recurring monthly savings scheme and is operated under the principle of Mudarabah. It is an Islamic financial partnership contract where one partner provides capital and the other provides labor. Income generated from the venture is distributed between the partners with a predetermined profit sharing ratio. The scheme is designed in such a way that people who desires to perform the Holy Hajj after a certain period can save &amp; get an attractive lump sum amount at the end of deposit period which is nearer to the expenditure to perform the Holy Hajj<br></font><ul><li><font face="Arial" size="3">This account is suitable for any Bangladeshi citizen above the age of 18 years</font></li><li><font face="Arial" size="3">No minimum balance is required</font></li><li><font face="Arial" size="3">No profit forfeiture</font></li><li><font face="Arial" size="3">Minimum installment and BDT 500/- only</font></li><li><font face="Arial" size="3">This account can be operated from 1 year to 20 years period</font></li></ul><font face="Arial" size="3"><br><font color="#330099"><b>Premature Closure:</b></font><br></font><ul><li><font face="Arial" size="3">No profit forfeiture</font></li><li><font face="Arial" size="3">Customer will get profit amount accrued for the completed years</font></li><li><font face="Arial" size="3">Customer will get profit amount @ SB rate for the months completed of running / current year</font></li></ul>'),
